Amanda Holden has put her incredible physique on display as she prepared for a game in skin-tight workout gear. The Heart FM radio host, 51, struck a series of sultry poses as she donned a white workout set to play tennis on a grass court. She flashed her flat stomach in view of her 1.8 million Instagram followers thanks to the cropped nature of the top, which also showcased her toned arms. Ever the fashionista, Amanda paired the white set with a pair of oversized black sunglasses. It comes as the star has been documenting her summer holdiays abroad in Greece and Italy, often sharing sizzling snaps of herself in swimwear.